  "title": "服务端渲染阵营九宫格",
  "summary": "你就说是不是渲染吧！",
  "content": "<blockquote><i></i> 这篇文章显然是经服务端渲染而呈现在你面前的。</blockquote>\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th></th>\n      <th>守序<div>一定要用 JS 框架渲染</div></th>\n      <th>中立<div>渲染出来的是 HTML 就行</div></th>\n      <th>混乱<div>渲染出来是图形就行</div></th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>善良</td>\n      <td><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/8e/Nextjs-logo.svg\"></td>\n      <td><img src=\"https://www.php.net/images/logos/php-logo.svg\"></td>\n      <td><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/20166026/230817316-92c7c746-0b5d-4307-90af-08bff113787e.png\"></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>一定要在<br>服务端渲染</td>\n      <td><div>守序善良</div> Next 是 SSR</td>\n      <td><div>中立善良</div> PHP 是 SSR</td>\n      <td><div>混乱善良</div> RDP 是 SSR</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>中立</td>\n      <td>\n        <div>\n          <img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:400/1*-8c5bXmKhpKg8NRnBMu0zQ.gif\">\n        </div>\n        <div><img src=\"https://pages.github.com/images/logo.svg\"></div>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <img>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <img>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>不在直接交互的<br>服务器上渲染也行</td>\n      <td><div>守序中立</div> SSG 是 SSR</td>\n      <td><div>绝对中立</div> CDN 是 SSR</td>\n      <td><div>混乱中立</div> OBS 推流是 SSR</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>邪恶</td>\n      <td>\n        <img src=\"https://www.electronjs.org/assets/img/logo.svg\">\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <img src=\"https://webassembly.org/css/webassembly.svg\">\n      </td>\n      <td>\n        <img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/6213c340453c3f502425776e/330e6487-af90-43c8-a255-63b3440d0e34/StabilityAi_Logo_White-19.png?format=1500w\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>用户的电脑<br>也是服务端</td>\n      <td><div>守序邪恶</div> Electron 是 SSR</td>\n      <td><div>中立邪恶</div> WASM 是 SSR</td>\n      <td><div>混乱邪恶</div> Stable Diffusion 是 SSR</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n<blockquote><i></i> 此 meme 受<span><span>梨咕米</span></span>启发而成。</blockquote><p></p>",
